name: Pongs Squad - Frutty Frut
description:
Pongs Squad is a group of criminals from an unknown country. They are scattered in various parts of the world due to a dispute between their captain and vice-captain.

Pas Covaz is the sniper of this group. He was nicknamed Frutty Frut because his skin was contaminated by the skin substance of the watermelon. Currently, he is hiding somewhere in Mexico.
